                  <summary><p>This manuscript of the <title xml:lang="sa">Hārītasmṛti</title> is the second in a <ref target="Sanscrit_0808.xml">collection</ref> of five <term xml:lang="sa">smṛti</term> texts. The text corresponds to that of the <title xml:lang="sa">Laghuhārītasmṛti</title> as edited by Shastri et al. (1952, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/smriti-sandarbha-gurumandal-series/Smriti%20Sandarbha%20Part%202%20-%20Gurumandal%20Series%201952/page/n433/mode/1up">974</ref>-<ref target="https://archive.org/details/smriti-sandarbha-gurumandal-series/Smriti%20Sandarbha%20Part%202%20-%20Gurumandal%20Series%201952/page/n453/mode/1up">994</ref>).</p>
</summary>
                  
